value.string: Well kept home in the Legends at Maui Lani. Wood floor downstairs. Comfortable home with central a/c. Short Sale has just been pre-approved by lienholder.

Darling new 3/2.5 home located at the much sought after Traditions subdivision in The Master planned community of Maui Lani, beautiful home with many upgrades, hunter Douglas plantation shutters throughout the home, Corian Counter tops, top of the line stainless steel appliances. 1st floor has high end wood laminate floors and carpet in the upstairs bedrooms. Pomaka'i Elementary School is within walking distance as well as a community park for the kids to play. Easy to show in short notice.

Better than new! This home has extensive and tasteful upgrades and shows like a model home ! The flooring in the entry, great room and kitchen has been replaced with top of the line Pergo XP, Koa laminate, with a lifetime warranty that looks and feels like hardwood. Designer paint, custom bamboo roman blinds,4 ceiling fans, soffit lighting, upgraded baseboards, stainless steel double sink, spotless appliances included along with upgraded washer and dryer, finished two car garage with storage cabinets and sink, 2 split Fujitsu a/c systems, solar hot water heater, up/down shades in the master, custom wooden blinds in guest bedrooms, which have ocean view. Back door phantom screens open up to your enclosed back yard. The back and front yard have been beautifully landscaped with native plants, perfect irrigation system with all plants having their own drip line, including an awesome papaya tree, banana, hibiscus, ginger, too many to count, providing privacy yet allow beautiful view of Mt. Haleakala. Zoysia lawn, stepping stones with extended covered lanai, dyed concrete, wrought iron and vinyl fencing with two gates, This is the best perimeter lot with views in the sought after neighborhood of Traditions at Maui Lani.

****CONVENIENT, CENTRAL LOCATION**** , Close to schools, Kaahumanu shopping Center, Medical facilities, parks, and county buildings. Very quiet culdesac , with cool ocean breezes and tropical roof style homes. Remodeled with new kitchen cabinets and granite counter tops, remodeled baths , new vanities, ceramic tiles, masterbath has deep jetted tub. No association fees or rules.

So warm and inviting, this lovely, impeccable Hawaiian style home is a show stopper! There's so many fine features to point out but lets start with the gorgeous pool! Rejuvenate, luxuriate and recharge your batteries everyday and night in this 15x30 heated pool. In our tropical climate you can use it all year round and the unique location allows you to use it in privacy as the pool fronts the Dunes Golf Course but is obscured by some Kiawe trees. It's always fun to have neighbors over for a barbecue at the pool under the spacious covered lanai while also enjoying views of the pristine lawn and tropical landscaping. Other features include new bamboo flooring and central air conditioning, solar heating system, an open airy kitchen with breakfast nook, en suite master bath with separate tub and shower, high ceilings, custom window treatments and tasteful soft colored walls. The location has easy access to the golf course, schools, shopping, hospital, restaurants and the airport. A must see property. Some furnishings may be included in the purchase. Can be shown with less than 24 hrs notice.

This is a wonderful, very well kept family home in an ideal location in Kahului. The bedrooms are all on the 2nd floor with a spacious master bedroom and bathroom along with 2 guest bedrooms and a guest bathroom. There's views from upstairs of Haleakala, West Maui mountains and a bit of ocean view. On the first level with the living, dining, kitchen and 2 car garage is a split AC system and solar heating system. New Traditions is very family oriented and there's an adorable children's park within the neighborhood that has a fun water feature for the kids. Directly across the street is the Pomaikai Elementary School and just about everything else is minutes away. The Dunes Golf Course and Restaurant is 2 minutes away, the hospital is 15 minutes away, the airport is just 12 minutes away and adjacent to this development is the big new sports complex that is being constructed. Easy to view with overnight notice. Priced to sell!
